add flag for file permission comparision (#197)

Two files can not only be compared by file content, but also by file
permissions. This is similar to file types (pipe, links, regular).

It is behind the command line option `-P` or `--permissions`

commit.message:
Set process exit code for shell in case of errors and file differences (#195)

Mimic the behavior of grep. Return 1 to the invoking shell if differences between the icdiff'ed files have been detected. Return 2 for bad arguments.
